307
00:17:48.400 --> 00:17:50.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Mungkin saya tanya selepas konsert.</i></c.bg_transparent>

308
00:17:51.361 --> 00:17:56.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Jika saya tak hati-hati,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>saya akan rosakkan perjumpaan mereka.</i></c.bg_transparent>

309
00:17:57.493 --> 00:17:58.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Tempat duduk depan,</i></c.bg_transparent>

310
00:17:59.620 --> 00:18:01.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>di dewan yang kecil,</i></c.bg_transparent>

311
00:18:01.455 --> 00:18:03.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Ren tentu akan nampak Nana.</i></c.bg_transparent>

312
00:18:04.041 --> 00:18:07.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Wanita yang awak tinggalkan</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>dalam kesedihan ada di depan awak.</i></c.bg_transparent>

313
00:18:07.836 --> 00:18:09.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Ren takkan dapat menahan dirinya.</i></c.bg_transparent>

314
00:18:10.589 --> 00:18:12.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Mereka berdua saling merenung.</i></c.bg_transparent>

315
00:18:12.883 --> 00:18:15.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Air mata Nana bergenang.</i></c.bg_transparent>

316
00:18:15.219 --> 00:18:18.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Ren akan terus lompat dari pentas</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>dan memeluk Nana.</i></c.bg_transparent>

317
00:18:19.640 --> 00:18:20.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Romantiknya.</i></c.bg_transparent>

318
00:18:21.475 --> 00:18:25.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Saya akan bertenang sehingga konsert itu</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>supaya Nana tak ubah fikiran.</i></c.bg_transparent>

319
00:18:25.729 --> 00:18:29.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Saya akan pura-pura tak tahu.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Saya dah dewasa.</i></c.bg_transparent>

320
00:18:29.233 --> 00:18:31.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Demi pertemuan semula mereka.</i></c.bg_transparent>

321
00:18:32.402 --> 00:18:37.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Baiklah, saya ikut saja cerita awak.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Lagipun, saya memang buat-buat tak tahu.</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:18:37.116 --> 00:18:38.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Terima kasih, Shin!</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:18:38.617 --> 00:18:42.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tapi saya cemburu.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Barisan depan? Kalaulah saya boleh pergi.</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:18:42.788 --> 00:18:44.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Betul. Maaf.</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:18:45.040 --> 00:18:49.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tapi saya tak pasti jika perjumpaan itu</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>seperti yang awak harapkan.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:18:49.211 --> 00:18:52.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Melompat dari pentas itu</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>hanyalah khayalan saya.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:18:52.631 --> 00:18:56.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Adakah Ren masih ada perasaan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>terhadap Nana?</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:18:57.261 --> 00:19:01.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Sudah dua tahun mereka tak berhubung.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Ya, saya tak pasti.</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:19:02.057 --> 00:19:03.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lagipun, lelaki itu…</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:19:03.475 --> 00:19:05.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dia lelaki jenis apa?</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:19:05.185 --> 00:19:08.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Khabarnya dia buaya darat.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Betulkah?</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:19:08.147 --> 00:19:11.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ya, tapi itu cerita lama.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:19:11.817 --> 00:19:14.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dia sangat setia kepada Nana.</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:19:14.736 --> 00:19:20.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lagipun Nana yang beri mangga</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>yang Ren selalu pakai itu.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:19:20.117 --> 00:19:23.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Biar benar. Yakah?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Maknanya, cinta dia masih ada.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:19:23.245 --> 00:19:26.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tapi dia mungkin pakai</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>kerana dia suka rupanya.</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:19:26.874 --> 00:19:29.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tak mungkin, mesti ada makna di situ.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:19:29.835 --> 00:19:31.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Awak setuju tak, Yasu?</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:19:34.089 --> 00:19:36.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ya, saya setuju.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:19:36.175 --> 00:19:37.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Saya dah agak!</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:19:40.846 --> 00:19:41.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kenapa?</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:19:41.930 --> 00:19:43.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mari mulakan latihan!</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:19:43.515 --> 00:19:44.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mari buat yang terbaik!</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:19:45.517 --> 00:19:47.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jangan patahkan semangat kami.</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:19:48.228 --> 00:19:50.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Ada dua minggu lagi sebelum konsert.</i></c.bg_transparent>

346
00:19:50.939 --> 00:19:54.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Hati saya berdebar-debar,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>tertanya-tanya jika Nana akan ubah fikiran</i></c.bg_transparent>

347
00:19:54.985 --> 00:19:57.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>sementara khayalan saya terus berkembang.</i></c.bg_transparent>

348
00:19:58.614 --> 00:20:00.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Jika Ren dan Nana kembali bersama,</i></c.bg_transparent>

349
00:20:01.074 --> 00:20:04.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>adakah bermakna ahli Tranes</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>akan lepak di rumah kami?</i></c.bg_transparent>

350
00:20:04.995 --> 00:20:07.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Jika begitu,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>saya boleh bercinta dengan Takumi.</i></c.bg_transparent>

351
00:20:07.664 --> 00:20:09.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Apa saya nak buat?</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:20:11.001 --> 00:20:12.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Apa halnya, Cik Komatsu?</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:20:35.651 --> 00:20:36.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Helo?</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:20:36.568 --> 00:20:38.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Saya. Ada. Di. Sini.</i></c.bg_transparent>

355
00:20:41.073 --> 00:20:42.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Awak lagi?</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:20:43.200 --> 00:20:45.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kenapa datang malam-malam begini?</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:20:47.579 --> 00:20:51.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Pada pagi hari konsert,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>awak berkelakuan macam biasa,</i></c.bg_transparent>

358
00:20:51.750 --> 00:20:53.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>duduk di tepi tingkap itu.</i></c.bg_transparent>

359
00:20:55.254 --> 00:20:58.173 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Tapi ada bau lain.</i></c.bg_transparent>

360
00:20:59.424 --> 00:21:01.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Rokok yang saya rampas daripada Shin.</i></c.bg_transparent>

361
00:21:02.344 --> 00:21:05.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Aroma Blackstone</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>yang saya sangka awak tak suka.</i></c.bg_transparent>

362
00:22:16.585 --> 00:22:18.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Terjemahan sari kata oleh Majdi Omar</c.bg_transparent>

